test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -3249 == -57
 +  where -3249 = <built-in function prod>([-3, -19, -57])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a1dc60968c0>([-57])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a1dc60968c0> = [[1, -57], [1, -57, 1], [-57, 1], [-57, 1, -57], [1, -57], [1, -57, 1], ...].count
